data.enText: a small electronic device that you carry around with you and that shows a message or lets you know when sb is trying to contact you, for example by making a sound

tr: an electronic device that generates a series of beeps when the person carrying it is being paged

value.def: A pager is a small electronic device which you can carry around with you and which gives you a number or a message when someone is trying to contact you.

value.boxr_value: in AM, usually use 美国英语通常用 beeper
